data.description: Location is Prime! Surrounded by green space and backing to single family homes. This offers privacy uncommon in a condo. Open & bright living area has been freshly painted, enjoy the gas fireplace this fall. Kitchen with updated lighting  has all appliances and a handy pantry. Main floor owners bedroom has a walk in closet & features full private bathroom. A second main floor bedroom possibility is currently used as a den. Upper story bedroom is HUGE! Full bath has been updated and has a walk in closet. Brand new furnace and central air in 2020. 1st floor laundry. Oversized 2 car garage. The private patio area is surrounded by perineal flowers. Plenty of available parking too. All exterior maintenance is taken care of in this well kept neighborhood! Close to shopping, restaurants & more.
